name: luddite
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "luddite" %}
{% set version = "1.0.2" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/luddite-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 8bec9f75247716320da307ff84df141b57fbd1f7e81a8bc2a7d7db88531cebc5

build:
  entry_points:
    - luddite=luddite:main
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  number: 3

requirements:
  build:
    - python                                 # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - cross-python_{{ target_platform }}     # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - colorama  # [win]
    - python
    - setuptools >=18.0

test:
  imports:
    - luddite
  commands:
    - pip list
    - pip check
    - luddite --help
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/jumptrading/luddite
  summary: Checks for out-of-date package versions
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - goanpeca
    - wimglenn
